import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; const Power = () => { const [showMore, setShowMore] = useState(false); const [currentLoad, setCurrentLoad] = useState(0); const [capacity, setCapacity] = useState(0); const [motorData, setMotorData] = useState({ frLoad: 0, flLoad: 0, brLoad: 0, blLoad: 0 }); const [jointData, setJointData] = useState({ j0Load: 0, j1Load: 0, j2Load: 0, j3Load: 0, j4Load: 0, eeLoad: 0 }); const [labLoadData, setLabLoadData] = useState({ x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, tray: 0, gripper: 0 }); const toggleMenu = () => { setShowMore(!showMore); }; useEffect(() => { const interval = setInterval(() => { // Function to generate random value in the range [-0.4, 0.4] with step 0.1 and rounded to 1 decimal place const getRandomValue = () => parseFloat((Math.random() * 0.8 - 0.4).toFixed(1)); setMotorData(prevMotorData => ({ frLoad: parseFloat(prevMotorData.frLoad) + parseFloat(getRandomValue()), flLoad: parseFloat(prevMotorData.flLoad) + parseFloat(getRandomValue()), brLoad: parseFloat(prevMotorData.brLoad) + parseFloat(getRandomValue()), blLoad: parseFloat(prevMotorData.blLoad) + parseFloat(getRandomValue()) })); setJointData(prevJointData => ({ j0Load: parseFloat(prevJointData.j0Load) + parseFloat(getRandomValue()), j1Load: parseFloat(prevJointData.j1Load) + parseFloat(getRandomValue()), j2Load: parseFloat(prevJointData.j2Load) + parseFloat(getRandomValue()), j3Load: parseFloat(prevJointData.j3Load) + parseFloat(getRandomValue()), j4Load: parseFloat(prevJointData.j4Load) + parseFloat(getRandomValue()), eeLoad: parseFloat(prevJointData.eeLoad) + parseFloat(getRandomValue()) })); setLabLoadData(prevLabLoadData => ({ x: parseFloat(prevLabLoadData.x) + parseFloat(getRandomValue()), y: parseFloat(prevLabLoadData.y) + parseFloat(getRandomValue()), z: parseFloat(prevLabLoadData.z) + parseFloat(getRandomValue()), tray: parseFloat(prevLabLoadData.tray) + parseFloat(getRandomValue()), gripper: parseFloat(prevLabLoadData.gripper) + parseFloat(getRandomValue()) })); }, 1000); return () => clearInterval(interval); }, []); return (
